title: Exato Technologies shares to list today. GMP hints at maximum premium on debut
description: Exato Technologies is set to list on the BSE SME platform. The company's initial public offering received an overwhelming response from investors. The issue was subscribed over 947 times. High net-worth individuals and retail investors showed strong interest.…
